{"tid":445492,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一定要好好珍惜身邊既人","createTime":"2017-10-23T12:30:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T04:12:48.000Z","uid":96977,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"738fcc28833ecc992238cfc15760116c65b24996","tid":445492,"uid":96977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T12:30:19.000Z","msg":"對住自己身邊既人 大家都可能已經習慣左用咩態度去面對<br />\n可能有時習慣到小左關心 態度唔好<br />\n但係所有野都可能嚟得好突然 <br />\n可能係突然之間就唔會再係到陪住你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後就後悔點解唔會夠啲關心 態度好啲咁去對佢地 陪多啲佢地<br />\n係仲有機會既時候 大家一定要好好珍惜身邊既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好因爲習慣而對得佢地唔好 唔珍惜佢地"},{"pid":"5e0c3272970576e35f4dd0ca6a7ba7e4db3ae0b4","tid":445492,"uid":154800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T12:52:52.000Z","msg":"但現實就係好多野無左你先覺得佢寶貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7bc2e24ffa8605d5cfa95d3b2a80b630d5a6801","tid":445492,"uid":92456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:39:32.000Z","msg":"人係犯賤嘅 永遠都係失去咗先知要珍惜"},{"pid":"e1c38942b9d8d75ec39fba78fb750c4a4bf9b9a1","tid":445492,"uid":12324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:12:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}